					<br /><br /><span class="profile_header">Child Profile</span><br /><p style="text-align: center;">MEET MACKENZIE</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Mackenzie is a quiet and somewhat shy 15 year old teen when she first meets you. Then she quickly warms up to show you her friendly personality.She enjoys playing games, watching movies, creating art and listening to music. And she is a huge animal lover. Mackenzie describes herself as "Optimistic," "Creative," "Smart" and "A Good Kid."</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Mackenzie is also a fashion-minded young lady who likes looking her best. Any family wanting to adopt Mackenzie will enjoy shopping with her to search for the right outfit.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Mackenzie enjoys school and is earning good grades.Mackenzie is currently a freshman in high school and plans to go to college after graduation. Mackenzie dreams of transferring her love of animals to becoming a Marine-Biologist when she grows up.</p>
