<p style="text-align: left;"></p><br /><br /><span class="profile_header">Desired Family</span><br /><p>Mackenzie's forever family will have a high level of experience and knowledge in parenting traumatized children. They will advocate for her, make sure she receives ongoing counseling and therapeutic services and provide her with unconditional love and support.</p></p>
				
				